
# Day 3 – SELECT Queries

## Topics Covered

- SELECT
- DISTINCT
- WHERE

## SELECT

Retrieve all columns.

```sql
SELECT *
FROM Student;
```

Retrieve specific columns.

```sql
SELECT name, age
FROM Student;
```

## WHERE

Filters rows.

```sql
SELECT *
FROM Student
WHERE age > 20;
```

## DISTINCT

Removes duplicate values.

```sql
SELECT DISTINCT department
FROM Employee;
```

